# Test Scenarios & Test Cases

## 1. Homepage Navigation & Links
### 1.1 Verify Home Page Loads
- Open `/`
- Validate page loads successfully (status 200)
- Ensure no console errors

### 1.2 Verify Important Links Exist
- Check presence of:
  - Privacy Policy
  - Documentation
  - GitHub repository
- Click each link and validate destination URL

### 1.3 Verify Hero Section & Image
- Validate banner is displayed
- Verify image has alt text
- Check footer text includes “DEMO application”

---

## 2. Product Listing
### 2.1 Verify Product Cards Rendering
- Each product card should display:
  - Name
  - Price
  - CO₂ label
  - Stock status

### 2.2 Verify Out-of-Stock Label
- At least one product shows “Out of stock”

### 2.3 Verify Filters UI
- Categories:
  - Hand Tools
  - Power Tools
  - Other
- Brand filter section should be visible

---

## 3. Search Behavior
### 3.1 Exact Search
- Search: `Pliers`
- Expected: At least one product displayed

### 3.2 Partial Search
- Search: `Ham`
- Expected: Products like “Hammer” shown

### 3.3 No Result Case
- Search: `xyzabc`
- Expected: “No products found” message

### 3.4 Case-Insensitive Search
- Search: `claw hammer`
- Expected: “Claw Hammer” displayed

---

## 4. Sorting
### 4.1 Default Sorting
- Verify default sort option is selected

### 4.2 Sort by Price (Low → High)
- Validate prices are in increasing order

### 4.3 Sort by Price (High → Low)
- Validate prices are in decreasing order

### 4.4 Sort by CO₂ Rating
- Validate correct order (A→E or E→A)

---

## 5. Filters
### 5.1 Single Category Filter
- Select “Hand Tools”
- Validate all results belong to this category

### 5.2 Multi-Category Filter
- Select “Hand Tools + Power Tools”
- Validate combined results only

### 5.3 Brand Filter
- Select a brand
- Validate all results match selected brand

### 5.4 Price Range Filter
- Set min + max values
- Validate products fall within range

### 5.5 Clear Filters
- Apply filters → clear all
- Validate full product list restored

---

## 6. Product Detail Page
### 6.1 Navigate to Product Detail
- Click product card
- Validate URL: `/product/<id>`

### 6.2 Verify Product Details
- Validate:
  - Name
  - Price
  - CO₂ label
  - Stock status
  - Description

### 6.3 Add to Cart Behavior
- In-stock → button enabled
- Out-of-stock → button disabled

### 6.4 Invalid Product Handling
- Open `/product/invalid`
- Validate 404 or error message

---

## 7. Cart & Checkout
### 7.1 Add Item to Cart
- Validate cart count updates

### 7.2 Remove Item
- Validate cart total updates

### 7.3 Cart Persistence
- Navigate across pages
- Validate cart retains items

### 7.4 Empty Cart Checkout
- Attempt checkout with empty cart
- Validate blocked

### 7.5 Successful Checkout
- Complete flow
- Validate success confirmation

